      <title>随着机构需求增长，更多对冲基金购买比特币 ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/more-hedge-funds-buy-bitcoin-etfs-as-institutional-demand-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着越来越多的传统投资者开始接受这一在美国监管机构的勉强帮助下于今年年初进入主流的资产类别，对冲基金、养老金和银行继续向直接投资比特币的交易所交易基金投入大量资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/more-hedge-funds-buy-bitcoin-etfs-as-institutional-demand-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 16:01:56 GMT</pubDate>
